# Binary robot mesh assets are stored via Git LFS to keep the repo lean and
# to stay under the pre-commit large-file guard. The trained policy weights
# (*.onnx) are intentionally committed directly (small, ~452 KB) and are NOT
# LFS-tracked.
*.stl filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.dae filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
